  <description><![CDATA[<p>Slovenia is a fabulously diverse country with dazzling lakes, colourful meadows and the stunning peaks of the Julian Alps. Create your perfect trip and combine contrasting resorts for a multi-centre holiday exploring our favourite lakes and scenic mountains in <a data-udi="umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049}" title="Slovenia">Slovenia</a>. The delightful journeys here take you through the most scenic parts of Slovenia with a wealth of walking and sightseeing opportunities for you to enjoy at your leisure.</p>
<h3>Your options for a multi-centre holiday in Slovenia: </h3>
<p>In Slovenia there are a variety of trips to choose from:</p>
<h4>Triple-centre holidays:</h4>
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type: none;">
<ul>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/a0191268612e4a3389b47a26550db553" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a0191268612e4a3389b47a26550db553}" title="Discover the Julian Alps">Discover the Julian Alps</a> - a 10-night trip to Bohinj, Bovec and Kranjska Gora</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h4>Standard multi-centre holidays: </h4>
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type: none;">
<ul>
<li>A variety of destination combinations are available</li>
<li>Flexible durations in each destination</li>
<li>Flexible arrival and departure days</li>
<li>Option to combine a stay in Slovenia with a stay in <a data-udi="umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760}" title="Austria">Austria</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3>Your holiday includes:</h3>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Return flights from the UK</li>
<li>Transfers from the airport to your hotel in your first destination, between destinations and from your hotel in your second destination to the airport</li>
<li>Accommodation in your chosen hotel in each destination</li>
</ul>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to Book Your Multi-Centre Holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Simply give us a call to book your multi-centre holiday. Flights, hotel and transport? Consider it done. Dial in and let our experts plan your dream getaway. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></description>
